Rong -- clone of computer game Pong (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pong), Rong means Wrong Pong.

Site: https://github.com/zlv/Rong

Authors: zlv(Yevgeny Lezhnin) <z_lezhnin@mail2000.ru>, pavertomato(Yegor Lezhnin) <pavertomato@gmail.com>, 2011 -- Tomsk->Siberia

Description:
You see 2 platforms painted with different colors, red and blue, you can control red one. There is a ball, that moving on the screen. There are 2 circle segments: red and blue too -- be carefull with them, because if a ball, then it has color different than your platform, falls on your segment, you will lose a point!

Controls:
You can control your platform with mouse clicking or arrow keys.

